        <c02 level="item" id="d1e235">
          <did>
            <unittitle><persname>Joseph Lincoln Steffens</persname>to the
                  Rev. 
                  <persname>Levi Moore Powers</persname>enclosing a 1
                  p. TLS, 1910 January 12, 
                  <persname>Joseph Fels</persname>to the Rev. 
                  <persname>L. M. Powers</persname></unittitle>
            <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">n.d.</unitdate>
            <physdesc>
              <genreform>ALS,</genreform>
              <extent>2 p.</extent>
            </physdesc>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>[Steffens hopes to meet the Rev. Powers in 
                  <geogname>Boston</geogname>. Acknowledges letter with
                  an article on 
                  <persname>Joseph Fels</persname>. Apologizes for
                  having mislaid another article in 
                  <geogname>New York</geogname>. On his return to 
                  <geogname>New York</geogname>he will see Mr. and Mrs.
                  Fels off. They are to go to 
                  <geogname>England</geogname>. ]</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
        <c02 level="item" id="d1e278">
          <did>
            <unittitle>(Enclosure: Fels to Powers)</unittitle>
            <unitdate era="ce" calendar="gregorian">1910 Jan 12</unitdate>
            <physdesc>
              <genreform>TLS,</genreform>
              <extent>1 p.</extent>
            </physdesc>
          </did>
          <scopecontent>
            <p>[Regards Fel's meeting with Steffens. Mentions
                  Steffens' admiration for Powers' library. Announces
                  his trip to 
                  <geogname>Boston</geogname>around February 12. Will
                  speak at the 
                  <corpname>20th Century Club</corpname>. Would like to
                  talk to many people who haven't heard "our message."
                  Urges him to meet with Steffens.]</p>
          </scopecontent>
        </c02>
      </c01>
